<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Closes Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, June 10 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at Tehran
Stock Exchange on Saturday closed at 2422.09 points, up 3.40 points
from Wednesday's finish.
</P>
<P>
A total of 3,159,598 shares changed hands in 1,626 deals and the
turnover stood at 14.25 billion rials (about 4.75 million U.S.
dollars).
</P>
<P>
The shares of 58 companies registered gains, while those of 30
others declined. 
</P>
