</P>
<P>
To confront terrorism, there must be a complete and continuous
policy of prevention which must be accompanied by a series of high
cost measures, Tsohatzopoulos said on the sidelines of the
European conference on peace, democracy and cooperation in the
Balkans, which began in Athens Saturday.
</P>
<P>
He added that they would not prove to be effective without the
existence of a policy of prevention.
</P>
