<HEADLINE> China Launches Website on Textile Industry </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, June 10 (Xinhua) -- Shanghai today launched China's
largest website on the textile industry.
</P>
<P>
The 50-million yuan website, at www.jwchina.com, was jointly
funded by the Huayuan Enterprise Development Shareholding Co. Ltd,
the China National Textiles Import and Export Corp., and the China
Chamber of Commerce of Imports and Exports of Textile, among
others.
</P>
<P>
Internet users can get a variety of information on China's
textile industry through the website's E-business platform.
</P>
