Wuhan, involving a total investment of 2 billion U.S. dollars.
France opened a general consulate in Wuhan in 1998, and the city
of Bordeaux forged sister-ties with Wuhan the same year.
</P>
<P>
There is a bright prospect for cooperation between France and
Hubei since the European Union signed an agreement with China on
China's entry into the World Trade Organization (WTO), French
officials said.  
