government helicopter, working in liaison with British forces,
dropped leaflets which warned of an impending offensive against
the rebels.
</P>
<P>
The Red Cross was reportedly providing some emergency aid to
the refugees in Mile 91 and the United Nations peacekeeping
missions was said to be preparing to arrange for more.
</P>
<P>
