LONDON, June 9 (Xinhua) -- England soccer team manager Kevin
Keegan has dismissed suggestions that he is covering up the truth
about captain Alan Shearer's knee injury.
</P>
<P>
The national skipper has been given a deadline of Sunday to
prove his fitness ahead of the opening game against Portugal.
</P>
<P>
Shearer has had a precautionary scan on the problem - but
