<HEADLINE> Mubarak Mourns Death of Assad </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CAIRO, June 10 (Xinhua) -- Egyptian President Hosni Mubarak
expressed deep sorrow for the death of Syrian President Hafez al-
Assad on Saturday, calling him a "close friend."
</P>
<P>
"President Mubarak received with deep sorrow the sad news of the
death of his close friend President al-Assad and always cherishes
the close friendship," a statement issued by the presidential
office said.
</P>
<P>
Assad "had made tremendous and valuable services not only to his
country but also to the Arab and Islamic nations," the statement
said.
</P>
<P>
